      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smooth, and is totally ready for a new adventure! It\u2019s been well-loved and is just looking for a great new home. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it!",
